
To build this project,you need the following packages and their development versions installed

KDE4
QT4
g++
cmake

To build the following commands in the source folder

mkdir build
cd build
cmake -DCMAKE_INSTALL_PREFIX=`kde4-config --prefix`  -DCMAKE_BUILD_TYPE=release  ..
make
make install ( or sudo make install )


To uninstall,run

make uninstall( or sudo make uninstall )